description: This skill gives you unique facts about soccer. When you ask Alexa the invocation name to open the skill, you then also have to ask Alexa to tell you a fact. Then only will it tell you a very interesting fact. These facts may surprise you and astound you!
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask amazing soccer facts to tell me a fact
Alexa ask amazing soccer facts to give me a fact
name: soccerfacts
shortDescription: This skill gives you unique and interesting facts about soccer, when you ask Alexa.
